**THE DETAILS IN THIS DASHBOARD ARE ESTIMATES, THE [DATA MANAGEMENT HUB](https://one.newrelic.com/launcher/data-management-nerdlets.data-management-launcher) SHOULD BE USED TO VIEW OFFICIAL INGESTION RATES**

This page analyzes data coming from the various [GCP integrations](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/integrations/google-cloud-platform-integrations/gcp-integrations-list/) available in New Relic. Data ingest for these integrations is most easily controlled in the individual service integration's [configuration settings](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/integrations/infrastructure-integrations/cloud-integrations/configure-polling-frequency-data-collection-cloud-integrations/).

*If you find a missing integration, please [open an issue](https://github.com/newrelic/newrelic-quickstarts/issues/new/choose) on our GitHub!*

nrqlQueries.query: SELECT sum(GigabytesIngested) AS '1 DAY (GB)', rate(sum(GigabytesIngested), 1 MONTH) AS '1 MONTH (GB)' FROM NrConsumption WHERE productLine='DataPlatform' AND usageMetric LIKE '%InfraIntegration%' LIMIT MAX SINCE 24 HOURS AGO COMPARE WITH 1 WEEK AGO

FROM GcpAppEngineServiceSample, GcpBigQueryTableSample, GcpBigQueryDataSetSample, GcpBigQueryProjectSample, 
GcpBigtableTableSample, GcpBigtableClusterSample, GcpCloudFunctionSample, GcpCloudSqlSample, 
GcpCloudTasksQueueSample, GcpComposerWorkflowSample, GcpComposerEnvironmentSample, GcpVirtualMachineSample, 
GcpVirtualMachineDiskSample, GcpDataflowJobSample, GcpDataprocClusterSample, GCPDatastoreRequestSample, 
GcpFirebasestorageBucketSample, GcpFirebasedatabaseNamespaceSample, GcpFirebasehostingDomainSample, GcpFirestoreRequestSample, 
GcpFirestoreInstanceSample, GcpInterconnectAttachmentSample, GcpInterconnectInterconnectSample, GcpKubernetesContainerSample, 
GcpKubernetesNodeSample, GcpKubernetesPodSample, GcpHttpLoadBalancerSample, GcpInternalLoadBalancerSample, 
GcpTcpSslProxyLoadBalancerSample, GcpMemcacheMemcacheNodeSample, GcpPubSubTopicSample, GcpPubSubSubscriptionSample, 
GcpRedisInstanceSample, GcpRouterCloudRouterSample, GcpRouterNatGatewaySample, GcpRunRevisionSample, 
GcpSpannerInstanceSample, GcpSpannerDatabaseSample, GcpStorageBucketSample, GcpVpcaccessConnectorSample
SELECT bytecountestimate()/10e8 AS '1 DAY (GB)', 
rate(bytecountestimate()/10e8, 1 MONTH) AS '1 MONTH (GB)' 
SINCE 24 HOURS AGO COMPARE WITH 1 WEEK AGO 
LIMIT MAX

FROM
GcpAppEngineServiceSample, GcpBigQueryTableSample, GcpBigQueryDataSetSample, GcpBigQueryProjectSample, 
GcpBigtableTableSample, GcpBigtableClusterSample, GcpCloudFunctionSample, GcpCloudSqlSample, 
GcpCloudTasksQueueSample, GcpComposerWorkflowSample, GcpComposerEnvironmentSample, GcpVirtualMachineSample, 
GcpVirtualMachineDiskSample, GcpDataflowJobSample, GcpDataprocClusterSample, GCPDatastoreRequestSample, 
GcpFirebasestorageBucketSample, GcpFirebasedatabaseNamespaceSample, GcpFirebasehostingDomainSample, GcpFirestoreRequestSample, 
GcpFirestoreInstanceSample, GcpInterconnectAttachmentSample, GcpInterconnectInterconnectSample, GcpKubernetesContainerSample, 
GcpKubernetesNodeSample, GcpKubernetesPodSample, GcpHttpLoadBalancerSample, GcpInternalLoadBalancerSample, 
GcpTcpSslProxyLoadBalancerSample, GcpMemcacheMemcacheNodeSample, GcpPubSubTopicSample, GcpPubSubSubscriptionSample, 
GcpRedisInstanceSample, GcpRouterCloudRouterSample, GcpRouterNatGatewaySample, GcpRunRevisionSample, 
GcpSpannerInstanceSample, GcpSpannerDatabaseSample, GcpStorageBucketSample, GcpVpcaccessConnectorSample
SELECT
bytecountestimate()/10e8
FACET CASES(
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpAppEngineServiceSample', 'GcpCloudTasksQueueSample', 'GcpCloudFunctionSample', 'GcpVirtualMachineSample', 'GcpVirtualMachineDiskSample', 'GcpKubernetesContainerSample', 'GcpKubernetesNodeSample', 'GcpKubernetesPodSample') AS 'Compute Services',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpBigQueryTableSample', 'GcpBigQueryDataSetSample', 'GcpBigQueryProjectSample', 'GcpComposerWorkflowSample', 'GcpComposerEnvironmentSample', 'GcpDataflowJobSample', 'GcpDataprocClusterSample', 'GcpPubSubTopicSample', 'GcpPubSubSubscriptionSample') AS 'Data and Analytics Services',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpBigtableTableSample', 'GcpBigtableClusterSample', 'GcpCloudSqlSample', 'GCPDatastoreRequestSample', 'GcpFirestoreRequestSample', 'GcpFirestoreInstanceSample', 'GcpMemcacheMemcacheNodeSample', 'GcpRedisInstanceSample') AS 'Database Services',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpFirebasedatabaseNamespaceSample', 'GcpFirebasehostingDomainSample', 'GcpFirebasestorageBucketSample') AS 'Mobile (Firebase) Services',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpHttpLoadBalancerSample', 'GcpInternalLoadBalancerSample', 'GcpTcpSslProxyLoadBalancerSample', 'GcpRouterCloudRouterSample', 'GcpRouterNatGatewaySample', 'GcpInterconnectAttachmentSample', 'GcpInterconnectInterconnectSample', 'GcpVpcaccessConnectorSample') AS 'Networking Services',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpStorageBucketSample') AS 'Storage Services'
)
SINCE 7 DAYS AGO TIMESERIES 
LIMIT MAX

FROM GcpAppEngineServiceSample, GcpBigQueryTableSample, GcpBigQueryDataSetSample, GcpBigQueryProjectSample, 
GcpBigtableTableSample, GcpBigtableClusterSample, GcpCloudFunctionSample, GcpCloudSqlSample, 
GcpCloudTasksQueueSample, GcpComposerWorkflowSample, GcpComposerEnvironmentSample, GcpVirtualMachineSample, 
GcpVirtualMachineDiskSample, GcpDataflowJobSample, GcpDataprocClusterSample, GCPDatastoreRequestSample, 
GcpFirebasestorageBucketSample, GcpFirebasedatabaseNamespaceSample, GcpFirebasehostingDomainSample, GcpFirestoreRequestSample, 
GcpFirestoreInstanceSample, GcpInterconnectAttachmentSample, GcpInterconnectInterconnectSample, GcpKubernetesContainerSample, 
GcpKubernetesNodeSample, GcpKubernetesPodSample, GcpHttpLoadBalancerSample, GcpInternalLoadBalancerSample, 
GcpTcpSslProxyLoadBalancerSample, GcpMemcacheMemcacheNodeSample, GcpPubSubTopicSample, GcpPubSubSubscriptionSample, 
GcpRedisInstanceSample, GcpRouterCloudRouterSample, GcpRouterNatGatewaySample, GcpRunRevisionSample, 
GcpSpannerInstanceSample, GcpSpannerDatabaseSample, GcpStorageBucketSample, GcpVpcaccessConnectorSample
SELECT bytecountestimate()/10e8
FACET CASES(
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpAppEngineServiceSample') AS 'App Engine',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpBigQueryTableSample', 'GcpBigQueryDataSetSample', 'GcpBigQueryProjectSample') AS 'BigQuery',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpBigtableTableSample', 'GcpBigtableClusterSample') AS 'Cloud Bigtable',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpCloudFunctionSample') AS 'Cloud Functions',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpCloudSqlSample') AS 'Cloud SQL',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpCloudTasksQueueSample') AS 'Cloud Tasks',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpComposerWorkflowSample', 'GcpComposerEnvironmentSample') AS 'Cloud Composer',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpVirtualMachineSample', 'GcpVirtualMachineDiskSample') AS 'Compute Engine',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpDataflowJobSample') AS 'Dataflow',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpDataprocClusterSample') AS 'Dataproc',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GCPDatastoreRequestSample') AS 'Datastore',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpFirebasestorageBucketSample') AS 'Firebase',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpFirebasedatabaseNamespaceSample') AS 'Firebase Database',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpFirebasehostingDomainSample') AS 'Firebase Hosting',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpFirestoreRequestSample', 'GcpFirestoreInstanceSample') AS 'Firestore',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpInterconnectAttachmentSample', 'GcpInterconnectInterconnectSample') AS 'Cloud Interconnect',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpKubernetesContainerSample', 'GcpKubernetesNodeSample','GcpKubernetesPodSample') AS 'Kubernetes Engine',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpHttpLoadBalancerSample', 'GcpInternalLoadBalancerSample', 'GcpTcpSslProxyLoadBalancerSample') AS 'Load Balancing',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpMemcacheMemcacheNodeSample') AS 'Memorystore',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpPubSubTopicSample', 'GcpPubSubSubscriptionSample') AS 'Pub/Sub',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpRedisInstanceSample') AS 'Memorystore for Redis',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpRouterCloudRouterSample', 'GcpRouterNatGatewaySample') AS 'Cloud Router',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpRunRevisionSample') AS 'Cloud Run',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpSpannerInstanceSample', 'GcpSpannerDatabaseSample') AS 'Cloud Spanner',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpStorageBucketSample') AS 'Cloud Storage',
WHERE eventType() IN ('GcpVpcaccessConnectorSample') AS 'Serverless VPC Access'
) OR eventType()
SINCE 7 DAYS AGO
TIMESERIES
LIMIT 25

FROM
	GcpAppEngineServiceSample,
	GcpCloudTasksQueueSample,
	GcpCloudFunctionSample,
	GcpVirtualMachineSample,
	GcpVirtualMachineDiskSample,
	GcpKubernetesContainerSample,
	GcpKubernetesNodeSample,
	GcpKubernetesPodSample
SELECT
bytecountestimate()/10e8 AS '1 DAY (GB)',
rate(bytecountestimate()/10e8, 1 MONTH) AS '1 MONTH (GB)'
SINCE 24 HOURS AGO COMPARE WITH 1 WEEK AGO
LIMIT MAX
